		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I find it awkward that all approved submappers are listed on a single entry and not on the corresponding mapper's entry. I think that a particular mapper's entry should list all information pertaining to it, including submappers, excluding only ASIC information shared among several mappers.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
